snippet: A Southern California woman who found a dead body in the trunk of her Lexus after shopping over the weekend discovered that the man was a neighbor, police said on Monday....

headline.print_headline: Woman Finds Body in Trunk, Learns It's Her Neighbor
headline.main: Woman Finds Body in Trunk, Learns It's Her Neighbor

lead_paragraph: A Southern California woman who found a dead body in the trunk of her Lexus after shopping over the weekend discovered that the man was a neighbor, police said on Monday.
